<h1> GET READY TO FIGHT: </h1>
<h2> <%= @turn.player_name %> vs Computer </h2>

<h3> Choose your weapon: </h3>

<form method="post" action="/lets_fight">
    <input type="submit" name="player_weapon" value="ROCK">
    <input type="submit" name="player_weapon" value="PAPER">
    <input type="submit" name="player_weapon" value="SCISSORS">
</form>

You picked <%= @turn.player_weapon %> as your weapon!

<div id="computer">
Computer has picked <%= @turn.computer_weapon.to_s.upcase %> as it's weapon!
</div>

<%= @turn.winner %> HAS WON!
